Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Builtin Dark"
Set Padding 20
Set LetterSpacing 1
Set LineHeight 1.2

Type "authmap --project tests/fixtures --interactive"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms

Type "?"
Sleep 2s

Type "?"
Sleep 400ms

Type "/"
Sleep 400ms
Type "admin"
Sleep 1.5s

Escape
Sleep 400ms
Type "q"
